      <section eId="sec_18_2_54">
        <num>18-2-54</num>
        <content>
          <p>The assignee shall succeed to all rights of the assignor but may attack and set aside any fraudulent conveyances or recover property conveyed by the assignor for the purpose of hindering, delaying, or defrauding creditors.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1894, p. 90, ยง 12; Civil Code 1895, ยง 2709; Civil Code 1910, ยง 3242; Code 1933, ยง 28-313.)</p>
